    {
      "chinese": "倉庫，播種祭時，會在這裡煮祭儀用的芋頭及占卜運勢，也是疏苗季後收藏農事用具的地方。另外，家屋居住空間不足時，可以做為已婚孩子的分家住屋。",
      "ab": "Ung at, maaz a langhaan hai dadangian mais lus’an mas BuanMinpinangcin mapit’ias tai tu na ispasutnul. Ung at, dadainpusas is’unhuhuma tu tanga minanavu mais mainatuis maduh. Ung at, sia tasa mas maupacin tu mais kaumanin a dangian mas tastulumahcin tu bunun hai mahtu amin a langhaan pin’unius na invaazan mas uvaaztan tu na dangian tu lumah.",
      "order": "3",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/27/7cecf722c8d4a33fe1be826c0c897889.wav",
      "word": [
        {
